{"tid":112630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Microsoft Keyboard + Mouse 點睇?","createTime":"2017-02-08T09:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T10:04:23.000Z","uid":81355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"753849047a31ab0475da957043d9d2df67e6a70a","tid":112630,"uid":81355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:34:18.000Z","msg":"想買無線keyboard + mouse<br />\n得閒打下單機GAME, 上網用<br />\n最鍾意攤係張床用電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMicrosoft Arc Touch Mouse<br />\n<img src=\"http://compass.microsoft.com/assets/b0/87/b0874914-01c8-43f2-91ad-3dae5deade63.jpg?n=Arc%20Touch%20Mouse.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcompass.microsoft.com%2Fassets%2Fb0%2F87%2Fb0874914-01c8-43f2-91ad-3dae5deade63.jpg%3Fn%3DArc%2520Touch%2520Mouse.jpg&h=4064afcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加<br />\n<br />\nMicrosoft All-in-One Media Keyboard<br />\n<img src=\"http://compass.microsoft.com/assets/4e/88/4e889f37-96dd-40e5-827a-284b7ec61739.jpg?n=hero.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcompass.microsoft.com%2Fassets%2F4e%2F88%2F4e889f37-96dd-40e5-827a-284b7ec61739.jpg%3Fn%3Dhero.jpg&h=91cd24eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點睇? 有冇巴打用緊, 比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用windows 7會唔會有限制?<br />\n<br />\n本身仲有隻Xbox one for windows手掣做後備<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁就儲晒成套同一牌子感覺好治癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd184a2af27de0458097b13d444427ccbbabd58","tid":112630,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:35:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c2f2d41c7aede1026035dccab6b2d262035c71b","tid":112630,"uid":81355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:39:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個mouse我有，幾好用<br />\n但中間果個碌碌唔係咁好用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網睇人開箱，話隻mouse 曲起左之後，因為中空<br />\n隻手指公同埋手指尾個感覺會好空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我比較擔心係，如果玩返d 射擊game<br />\n個left click 同 right click 會唔會唔好禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01d88dc05e51c2cdfb1f3e3c539fc21e6860d7f","tid":112630,"uid":5604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:54:15.000Z","msg":"Mouse幾好用，left right click都好禁<br />\n係中間個碌碌有d嘈，用得長時間隻手會有小小攰<br />\n<br />\n利申 用左5年+"},{"pid":"b058a0f4aba7917b6fbec28c90d19cf8fbc68b91","tid":112630,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T09:56:10.000Z","msg":"無線keyboard 有D型號冇開關"},{"pid":"9fd51168f835367327e75e1330700a2207b22634","tid":112630,"uid":81355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T10:04:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無線keyboard 有D型號冇開關</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打我見我想買果隻有開關<br />\n同埋貪佢側邊有pad 又可以當mouse 用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過未用過唔肯定個pad如何<br />\n<br />\n加上上網睇人講又話win7有d手勢用唔到<br />\n但價錢勝在抵吊 ($289) <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}